import pandas
import seaborn

Populating the interactive namespace from numpy and matplotlib

This is my first attempt at using Jupyter Notebook, I have followed a number of tutorials to learn the basics. I used two data sets, one from September's Uber Data and one from April's Uber Data. I chose those two as there would clearly be differences in frequency of rides because of the change in temperature, allowing for a simple analysis for my first time!¶

In [29]:
def get_dom(dt):
    return dt.day
datasept['dom'] = datasept['Date/Time'].map(get_dom)
dataapr['dom'] = dataapr['Date/Time'].map(get_dom)
In [30]:
def get_weekday(dt):
    return dt.weekday()
datasept['weekday'] = datasept['Date/Time'].map(get_weekday)
dataapr['weekday'] = dataapr['Date/Time'].map(get_weekday)
In [31]:
def get_hour(dt):
    return dt.hour
datasept['hour'] = datasept['Date/Time'].map(get_hour)
dataapr['hour'] = dataapr['Date/Time'].map(get_hour)

def count_rows(rows):
    return len(rows)
by_cross_hw_sept = datasept.groupby('weekday hour'.split()).apply(count_rows).unstack()
In [37]:
by_cross_hw_apr = dataapr.groupby('weekday hour'.split()).apply(count_rows).unstack()
